{"tid":1390371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家一齊入黎睇下著名音樂劇孤星淚(Les Miserable)既劇情","createTime":"2019-07-31T06:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T05:26:19.000Z","uid":149494,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"052bea4830deabfbf1afc919174f67b7b261322d","tid":1390371,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:29:41.000Z","msg":"權貴用盡一切歪理同不公手段去管治、欺壓百姓<br />\n警察協助權貴維穩<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2012/12/25/arts/jpmiserables/jpmiserables-jumbo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2012%2F12%2F25%2Farts%2Fjpmiserables%2Fjpmiserables-jumbo.jpg&h=1d0c8d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以屈人偷面包，再判你坐十九年監<br />\n<img src=\"https://wp-media.patheos.com/blogs/sites/44/2012/12/les-mis-valjean-convict-5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwp-media.patheos.com%2Fblogs%2Fsites%2F44%2F2012%2F12%2Fles-mis-valjean-convict-5.jpg&h=8ed7ea96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一班年青人對社會現況看不過眼，站起來反抗<br />\n<img src=\"https://secure.i.telegraph.co.uk/multimedia/archive/02446/LesMis_rables_2446250b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.i.telegraph.co.uk%2Fmultimedia%2Farchive%2F02446%2FLesMis_rables_2446250b.jpg&h=fa9f3de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察覺得自己係執行公義，維護法治，誓要剷除一切不法份子<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hRzvdQh8D2Q/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FhRzvdQh8D2Q%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=5c462612&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另有班人於亂世中借依附權貴同警察搵食<br />\n<img src=\"http://stagedoordish.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Masters-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstagedoordish.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F03%2FMasters-1.jpg&h=409d2ef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年青人終於忍唔住，要同班權貴來場終極一戰<br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/60f1efbe482f732a6845faca38132e8e/tumblr_pl8hvqKSLX1w0lutwo5_r1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F60f1efbe482f732a6845faca38132e8e%2Ftumblr_pl8hvqKSLX1w0lutwo5_r1_500.gif&h=c2694221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察混入人群，找機會瓦解年青人的行動<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/68/33/08/6833083ae1ca03511b1ff467ff511395.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F68%2F33%2F08%2F6833083ae1ca03511b1ff467ff511395.jpg&h=00368ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結局︰<br />\n年青人的力量有限，以卵擊石下慘死<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/lesmiserables/images/0/07/The_Final_Battle.png/revision/latest?cb=20130715153112\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Flesmiserables%2Fimages%2F0%2F07%2FThe_Final_Battle.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20130715153112&h=ed58d211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n怕事的一般百姓於年青人抗爭時沒有出來幫忙，在他們死後才走出來表現喪傷<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/lesmiserables/images/0/0d/Turning.png/revision/latest?cb=20130716133218\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Flesmiserables%2Fimages%2F0%2F0d%2FTurning.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20130716133218&h=a565eab2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab618aaa8afecee23ac0ace93a07e17da965bedd","tid":1390371,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:34:29.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"7694bb6f11446da7b5fff39cca66aaa06934c496","tid":1390371,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:37:22.000Z","msg":"香港已死"},{"pid":"56958e10b9d3994776bdbffd0b38d94d2def8113","tid":1390371,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7694bb6f11446da7b5fff39cca66aaa06934c496","tid":1390371,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:37:22.000Z","msg":"香港已死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/